<Content>Fantastic Of all the hotels we stayed in during our two month trip, we rate this hotel most highly.Check in was handled seamlessly, the staff were helpful and informative. We paid a rate of Euro 80 per night and could not get over the value for money. It was excellent.The total experience was very positive. Excellent room, bathroom, facilities, cleanliness, location, price. It scored full marks on all counts.Breakfast was amazing. Wall to wall food choices with every taste catered for.The bus directly to the (TXL) airport departs from the road (lt Moabit) directly behing the hotel.When we go back to Berlin, that is where we shall stay. Highly recommended. 
