<Author>okazon69
<Content>Nice modern hotel, convenient location, fantastic breakfast The hotel is a 10-minute taxi ride from Tegel airport, and a 5-minute walk from the nearest S-Bahn station, from where you can get to many places in Berlin within a short time. The standard rooms are average in size, but very clean and comfortable. The bathrooms have the typical German efficiency to them - no luxurious touches here. The breakfast buffet is fantastic - choices galore, though the typical North American traveller will miss some items. Live a little, and go the European way! The staff are very helpful, and will gladly try to help with any extra requests you may have.The price for the hotel is usually quite decent, given the quality and location. 
